cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is primarily focused on face recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The use of deep learning models for face recognition also suggests that it could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The generation of synthetic data involves 3D modeling, which could also place it under multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) categories.
